result.name: Nahm, Vietnamese & Thai

reviews.text: This restaurant located in Elements,  quite a lot of ppl have lunch and dinner there, booking ahead is recommended. The environment is nice but the services is just so so compare before. l love the garlic bread  to go with curry, the shrimp spring roll, beef noodles...... will come again.

It's ok. Tasty, cheap, always a line. Good. Nothing memorable. Just sold Thai food. My papaya salad was a bit too soggy. My seabass was perfectly most and even slightly crispy which I loved but, again, there was just too much sauce which drowned out the taste of the fish (in this case, curry).

Nice food and I like their lunch set. You can choose a salad and a main course. For salad i do not recommend green papaya salad as it is far from traditional taste. It would be nice if a drink is included in the lunch set as their water taste like tap water.... Overall is good and will visit again!
Consistently good food. Pleasant service.
One of our favorite Vietnamese restaurants in town . Great food , nice evironment and friendly staff. Also located in convenient Elements mall.

reviews.text: 首先，我覺得這家餐廳的服務員態度非常好，而且非常禮貌，值得一讚。食物水平就十分驚悚。點了一份香辣牛肉炒河粉，讓我難忘。牛肉十分堅硬，很難咬開、加上有點涼掉了，可見是一早煮好放一邊納涼。河粉一早已經糊在一起。芡汁的溫度很明顯是不夠熱的，上面浮出一層油。加上只是淋上河粉，跟河粉根本是兩個味道，也因為如此，淋在菜上感覺有點油膩。最後，既然是香辣，所以有幾顆辣椒陪襯，也因為是陪襯，感覺不到這碟河粉有辣味。其實我想當下跟經理發表一下意見，但就算再上一碟，可能進步空間也不大，還是下次去其他地方吃好了
點了豬頸肉、沙爹牛、泰式鮮卷沙律🥗⋯還有推薦的雞尾酒🍸⋯整體味道沒有泰式特有的酸辣⋯沙爹也沒有味道、只有鹹味⋯也吃不出是哪國的料理味道⋯很失望的！

This restaurant located in Elements,  quite a lot of ppl have lunch and dinner there, booking ahead is recommended. The environment is nice but the services is just so so compare before. l love the garlic bread  to go with curry, the shrimp spring roll, beef noodles...... will come again.
越泰食品😋😋 價格合理 環境舒適寧靜 + 服務 👍👍
